title: S7E11 – "The Depravity" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you five spine-chilling tales from author C.J. Cannatelli, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about fear-filled families, cryptic creatures, ominous occupations, awful addictions, and deadly decisions.
